item.title: CVE-2021-34427|2024-08-04T00:12:50.360Z -- the%20eclipse%20foundation -- eclipse%20birt
item.description: In Eclipse BIRT versions 4.8.0 and earlier, an attacker can use query parameters to create a JSP file which is accessible from remote (current BIRT viewer dir) to inject JSP code into the running instance.
